OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with showers, these
OL,7,Fheavy at first but gradually easing. A
OL,8,Ffew clear intervals in east overnight
OL,9,Fbefore outbreaks of rain reaching
OL,10,FLochaber around midnight extend
OL,11,Fnortheast overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain, this turning heavy at times. A
OL,15,Ffew limited brighter intervals in the
OL,16,Feast, where it could be quite warm.
OL,17,FMore showery in evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
