OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy Tuesday but with bright
OL,7,Fintervals and showers. Bright spells
OL,8,Fand showers on Wednesday. Mostly
OL,9,Fcloudy with showers on Thursday.
OL,10,FBreezy Wednesday and Thursday.
